npm install --save @google-cloud/text-to-speech dotenv fs
```

2. Create a Google Cloud Platform account and set up a new project. Follow the instructions [here](https://cloud.google.com/text-to-speech/docs/quickstart-client-libraries) to enable the Text-to-Speech API and create an API key.

